<h2>Installation Guide</h2>

- Install lift.bot library `pip install lift.bot`
- Create `main.py`

<h2>Examples</h2>

```py
from lift import lft

# Example command
@lft.bot.command()
async def hi(ctx):
    await ctx.reply(f"Hey, {ctx.author.name}")

lft.login("token")
```
